      == Usage question

      Our friendly volunteer community regularly answers jBPM questions on StackOverflow. To get a helpful answer, follow https://stackoverflow.com/help/how-to-ask[the StackOverflow guidelines] such as:

      * Get to the point. Keep it short.
      * Be crystal clear. Reread your question before posting it.
      * Add relevant technical details: stacktrace, code snippet, ...

